pr_body: This is the demo scenario I have been working on as part of Google Summer of Code. The map is a reduced version and the full version can be accessed [here](https://github.com/MakinoharaShouko/hotel). The full map consumes a huge amount of memory thus cannot run. This version is reduced so that the rmf_core can handle most requests. Though It still breaks when the request is long (especially for the MiR100 fleet)
